\-Returns the application's main settings object. 

\-You can use it to retrieve or set application wide settings (in contrast to session or project specific settings).

\-If {\itshape scope\/} is \-Q\-Settings\-::\-User\-Scope (the default), the users settings will be read from the users settings, with a fallback to global settings provided with \-Qt \-Creator.

\-If {\itshape scope\/} is \-Q\-Settings\-::\-System\-Scope, only the system settings shipped with the current version of \-Qt \-Creator will be read. \-This functionality exists for internal purposes only.

\-Returns the application's main settings object. 

\-You can use it to retrieve or set application wide settings (in contrast to session or project specific settings).
